This study is a 5-year continuation of "The Mediterranean Lifestyle Program.

" The purpose of this follow-up study is to determine the long-term effects from prior participation in an intervention promoting healthful eating, exercise, quitting smoking, stress management, and social support.

 Participants are post-menopausal women with type 2 diabetes.

